 25/2/18 Sell here rode out through Quesqu on to the Ecouevill ridg from which a magnific view is to be had . Walk all over this and decid on a plan for our attack practic . Back to BnH.Q . and tri a number of case of overstay leav which offenc is becom altogeth too frequent . Old Crowley revert to rank of Corpor at his own request . Fix up some routin matter . My host at the billet complain of tree cut up and use by our men for fire and has claim 100 franc therefor . This will be paid by the men concern Our new Padr ( Smith ) was in to mess . Held a confer of offic afterward .
